<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Password Reset Request</h1>
    <p>
      Hello <%= @user.name %>,
    </p>
    <p>
      We received a request to reset your password for your FolioFlux account.
      To reset your password, please use the following code:
    </p>
    <div style="padding: 10px; background-color: #f5f5f5; font-size: 24px; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; letter-spacing: 5px;">
      <strong><%= @verification_code %></strong>
    </div>
    <p>
      This code will expire in 1 hour.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact support if you have concerns.
    </p>
    <p>
      Thanks,<br>
      The FolioFlux Team
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
